data.description: Welcome to the home of your dreams in West Lancaster. This upgraded 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom single story home offers a private courtyard at the entrance, providing the perfect spot to enjoy both sunrise and sunset moments.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious great room featuring a vaulted ceiling, wood-look tile flooring, two-toned interior paint, and a cozy gas fireplace. The open floorplan seamlessly flows from the great room into the oversized dining room, adorned with designer light fixtures and a sliding glass door leading to the backyard. The dining room connects to a light and bright kitchen, showcasing a large center island, quartz countertops, white cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, and a charming farmhouse sink. With direct access to the backyard, it's an ideal space for both cooking and entertaining. The primary bedroom is a haven of comfort, offering vaulted ceilings, a ceiling fan, and a sliding glass door to the backyard. An attached primary bathroom features dual sinks, a vanity area, a separate soaking bathtub, a shower, and an oversized walk-in closet. Three secondary bedrooms, each with ceiling fans and spacious closets, share a secondary bathroom with a large vanity and bathtub/shower combination. Conveniently, there's an indoor laundry room with shelving and direct access to the attached 2-car garage. The backyard is a sanctuary, featuring a beautiful patio cover that spans the length of the house, an above-ground pool, and block wall fencing. Extended concrete in the front and back of the house enhances the driveways' space. This move-in-ready home has been thoughtfully upgraded inside and out, including owned solar panels. Don't miss the opportunity to make this fantastic cul-de-sac corner lot home yours!
